        "body": "## Summary\n- add a Gradium realtime transcription provider and register it through the plugin manifest\n- cover provider behavior with focused tests and plugin registration checks\n- update Gradium voice/media docs, plugin inventory docs, and changelog\n\n## Testing\n- git diff --check upstream/main\n- node scripts/generate-plugin-inventory-doc.mjs --check\n- node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/gradium/plugin-registration.contract.test.ts extensions/gradium/realtime-transcription-provider.test.ts\n- pnpm tsgo:extensions\n- pnpm tsgo:extensions:test\n- pnpm lint:extensions\n- pnpm lint:extensions:bundled\n- pnpm run test:extensions:package-boundary:compile\n- pnpm run test:extensions:package-boundary:canary\n\n## Real behavior proof\nBehavior addressed: Gradium realtime STT now requires explicit Voice Call STT selection or provider config before `GRADIUM_API_KEY` can make it eligible, while explicit Gradium STT configuration still streams real audio through the Gradium realtime ASR WebSocket path.\n\nReal environment tested: Local OpenClaw checkout on macOS, Node 22, with a real Gradium API key loaded from local shell config. The secret value was not printed.\n\nExact steps or command run after the patch: Ran `OPENCLAW_LIVE_TEST=1 node scripts/test-live.mjs -- extensions/gradium/gradium.live.test.ts` after commit `b6bbc5e46a5fcc96f0b2d442cc7fc38fda253775`.\n\nEvidence after fix: Copied live terminal output from the real Gradium run:\n\n```text\nRUN  v4.1.7 /Users/pratimbhosale/Desktop/workspace/openclaw\n\nAudio written to /var/folders/y6/ghp5ytg96j14fcm1z0dtrw4m0000gn/T/gradium-live-test.wav\n\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  2 passed (2)\nStart at  14:50:56\nDuration  12.76s (transform 4.36s, setup 245ms, import 5.69s, tests 6.75s, environment 0ms)\n```\n\nObserved result after fix: The real Gradium TTS call generated audio, wrote `gradium-live-test.wav`, and the real Gradium realtime STT provider completed the streaming transcription flow successfully.\n\nWhat was not tested: No additional gaps.\n",
